    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TRANS WORLD AIRLINES, INC.\nLos Angeles International Airport\nLos Angeles 9, California\nJune 11, 1963\nMiss Audrey McNamara\nHostess\nTrans World Airlines, Ince\nLos Angeles, California\nDear Audrey:\nI am very pleased that you have finally been released\nto return to duty.\nIt has been a long siege and one\nthat I know has been most unpleasant for you.\nWe have been most appreciative of your fine attitude\nduring this periode\nWelcome back,\nF. L. Austin\nDistrict Transportation Mgr. - Flying\nFLA :HM\ncc: Miss Doris J. Owen",
      "Miss Audrey McNamara\nHostess\nTrans World Airlines, Inc.\nLos Angeles, California"
    ],
